## 技术架构

```
AI 返回内容
    │
    ▼
StreamingResponseParser (agents_service.dart)
    │ 检测行前缀 C>/B>/W>/N>
    │
    ├─► C> → onText() → fullContent → 聊天框
    ├─► B> → onBlackboard() → streamingBlackboardContent → 黑板
    ├─► W> → onWorkbook() → streamingWorkbookContent → 做题册
    └─► N> → onNotebook() → streamingNotebookContent → 笔记本
```

